Class SubmitResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.etrzby.xml.OdpovedType
      • cz.tomasdvorak.eet.client.dto.SubmitResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SubmitResult
extends OdpovedType
    Communication result holding all response data and additionally also all request data. There are defined some additional helper methods for easier access to usual fields (FIK, PKP, BKP)
